text: National Student Loan Service Centre (NSLSC) - Passcode Grid This is your personal NSLSC Passcode Grid. You should save and/or print it for your records. You will be prompted to enter specific grid values every time you sign in to NSLSC. Save as PDF Print Passcode Grid: NSLSC Serial number of your Passcode Grid: 034840 Expiry date of your Passcode Grid: August 16, 2026 Ensure you save and/or print your Passcode Grid before continuing. Keep your Passcode Grid safe and avoid sharing it.
